title: DAZ3D - Beyond the Clock
description:
A complete inside of a clock tower for daytime scene

3 levels of sets

2 preloads sets in Iray and 3Delight

10 cameras

Easy to be used with day ambiance thanks to optimized lights settings for Iray and 3delight props, side and exterior wall that can be removed to make it easier to set up scenes or to close the set

Separated gears and hands clock movable and modular

57 gears already animate or ready for your animation!
 
http://www.daz3d.com/beyond-the-clock
